article.description: — Antonio TJ Madlock registered 18 points and eight rebounds as South Carolina State beat The Citadel 74-57 on Monday night.
article.headline: Madlock scores 18 to carry SC State past The Citadel 74-57
article.linkText: Madlock scores 18 to carry SC State past The Citadel 74-57
article.story: CHARLESTON, S.C. -- — Antonio TJ Madlock registered 18 points and eight rebounds as South Carolina State beat The Citadel 74-57 on Monday night. Cameron Jones had 11 points for South Carolina State (6-8). Jemel Davis added 11 points and three blocks. Deaquan Williams had seven rebounds. Hayden Brown had 26 points and 14 rebounds for The Citadel (6-4). Stephen Clark added three blocks. Tyler Moffe had six assists. South Carolina State evened the season series against The Citadel. The Citadel defeated South Carolina State 91-79 on Nov. 28. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
